    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. can you get more specific though? like, if i'm writing this for people who want to reach that top-tier level of \"professionalism,\" what are the actual gold standards for stuff like dress codes and communication styles? i want to give them a clear blueprint of what the global standard for sophistication actually looks like.",
